txt.en: 'Oh no! I left my hat at home! I'd better go and get it.'
'Oh no! I left my handkerchief at home! I'd better go and get it.'
'Oh no! I left my walking stick at home! I'd better go and get it.'
'Belgo! Get down from there at once!'
'And I make it to the end again!'
'You're going to hurt yourself, Belgo!'
'No one can balance like me!'
'I wish Ruby and Bingo were here to see how fast I can do this!'
'Watch your step, Belgo! Honestly!'
'Not even a Took or a Brandybuck could best me at this!'
'I have the best balance of any hobbit in the Shire!'
'You're going to fall if you aren't careful!'
'If you don't come down from there right this instant....'
'One more run along the wall!'
'I don't want you up there, Belgo!'
'No one has better balance than I do!'
'You get down from there, Belgo!'
'I'll run even faster this time!'
'Oh no! I left my wallet at home! I'd better go and get it.'
'I'm the fastest runner in the Northfarthing!'
